  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The Motus GI Colon Cleansing device is intended to facilitate intra-procedural cleaning of a
      poorly prepared colon by irrigating the colon and evacuating the irrigation fluid and feces.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
